description:
On today’s show, Emily talks about how you can’t let a bad experience during sex scar you forever – because the first time is not always the best time and second chances aren’t always a bad thing.

Plus, why you should stop gossiping about your partner’s sexual exploits, threesome etiquette, and what the heck to do when your partner loves their vibrator, but you both want to have a big O without it.
